---
title: Mexican Pork & Black Bean Tostadas with Yoghurt & Cheddar Cheese
description: To make this meal come together in a jiffy, we started with the classic Mexican dish of tostadas! In Mexican cuisine, tostadas are piled high with ingredients and eaten like an open sandwich. We've topped ours with a spicy veggie-packed pork chilli, plus cooling yoghurt and Cheddar for a quick and satisfying dinner.

*Unfortunately, this week's coriander was in short supply, so we've replaced it with spring onion. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
